natives Considered\" table, lines 96-103)\n\n| Alternative | Decision | Reason |\n|-------------|----------|--------|\n| **Operator-based deployment** | **Deferred** | Consider if AgentCube adopts GitOps patterns requiring custom operators |\n| **Helm `apiVersion: v2`** | **Deferred** | Use `v1` now, upgrade to `v2` if subchart/library dependencies are added |\n\n### 5. Follow-up Changes (from design.md Section 7, lines 789-798)\n\n| Change | Dependency | Description |\n|--------|------------|-------------|\n| CRD YAML自动生成 | Depends on `make gen-crd` | Auto-generate CRDs from Go types kubebuilder markers |\n| Helm 单元测试 (helm-unittest) | Depends on AR-030 completion | Introduce helm-unittest plugin for automated testing |\n| Helm 3 apiVersion v2 升级 | Depends on AR-030 completion | Upgrade to v2 if subchart/library chart support needed |\n| 生产级 values 覆盖文件 | Depends on AR-030 completion | Create staging/production values-override.yaml files |\n| Helm 仓库发布 | Depends on AR-030 completion | `helm package` + `helm push` to OCI registry or ChartMuseum |\n| GitOps 集成 (ArgoCD/Flux) | Depends on AR-030 completion | Manage chart as HelmRepository + HelmRelease in GitOps |\n\n### 6. Git Commit History\n\nNo git commits were found with \"AR-030\" in the commit message. Two commits reference Helm-related work:\n- `84e4858` -- \"Regenerate specs from source code (298->1906 lines)\"\n- `6c48f1d` -- \"Complete SDD benchmark: full project generation + validation + reports\"\n\n### 7. Complete File Inventory\n\nAll files related to AR-030 / Helm Chart / manifests / agentcube:\n\n```\nchanges/AR-030/proposal.md                                          (117 lines)\nchanges/AR-030/design.md                                            (798 lines)\nchanges/AR-030/delta-spec.md                                        (402 lines)\nchanges/AR-030/tasks.md                                             (322 lines)\nmanifests/charts/base/Chart.yaml                                    (5 lines)\nmanifests/charts/base/values.yaml                                   (65 lines)\nmanifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml        (227 lines)\nmanifests/charts/base/crds/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_codeinterpreters.yaml     (150 lines)\nmanifests/charts/base/templates/_helpers.tpl                        (45 lines)\nmanifests/charts/base/templates/workloadmanager.yaml                (76 lines)\nmanifests/charts/base/templates/agentcube-router.yaml               (79 lines)\nmanifests/charts/base/templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml           (149 lines)\nmanifests/charts/base/templates/rbac-router.yaml                    (42 lines)\nmanifests/charts/base/templates/volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml  (296 lines)\ntest/chart/test_render.sh                                           (271 lines)\n```\n\n### 8. Implementation Status Summary\n\nThe **tasks.md** file shows all tasks as unchecked (`[ ]`), meaning the task list is a specification of what needs to be done. However, the actual implementation files in `manifests/charts/base/` are fully present and match the design specification -- all templates, CRDs, values, helpers, and the test script exist and are complete. The status checkboxes in `proposal.md` (`[ ] Proposal review`, `[ ] Implementation`, `[ ] Verification`) remain unchecked, suggesting the formal workflow tracking has not been updated even though the code artifacts are in place.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_285c8171affeuulVuJ1St6RL0O","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Find AR-030 archive info","time":{"start":1775871977699,"end":1775872091245}}}}
